Package: spelling
Title: Tools for Spell Checking in R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeroen", "Ooms", , "jeroen@berkeley.edu", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Jim", "Hester", , "james.hester@rstudio.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Spell checking common document formats including latex, markdown, manual 
    pages, and description files. Includes utilities to spell automate spell checking
    R package documentation and vignettes as a unit test during CMD check.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  commonmark,
  xml2, 
  hunspell,
  knitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
